sequenceDiagram
participant User
participant TextField
participant SaveButton
participant NoteStorage
participant Page

User->>TextField: Write a new note
Note right of User: The user writes a note in the text field

User->>SaveButton: Click "Save"
Note right of the User: The user clicks the "Save" button

SaveButton->>NoteStorage: Save the new note
NoteStorage-->>Page: Confirm note saved
Note right of the SaveButton: The note is saved in the storage system

Page-->User: Display new note
Note right of the Page: The page confirms that the note is saved and displays it to the user
